title: The Outsider’ E9. Plus: What Does the Netflix Top 10 Teach Us? | The Watch
description:
Chris and Andy review the penultimate episode of ‘The Outsider’ (SPOILERS) (0:55), before trying to glean meaning from a new feature on Netflix—its top-10 most popular list (29:10).

Hosts: Chris Ryan and Andy Greenwald
